# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
REQUESTS.local.md
CONTINUE_PROMPT.local.md
*.local.md
AGENTS.md
**/AGENTS.md
DEAD_CODE_AUDIT.md
HANDOFF.md
DESIGN.md
